## Secrets (never commit)
CLAUDE-secrets.md
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
# Allow the committed prod-env TEMPLATE, but never the real filled-in stack env.
!deploy/.env.prod.example
stack.env
/root/stack.env

# ── SOPS secrets management ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Commit ONLY the age-encrypted *.enc.yaml + the docs/helper. Block everything
# else under secrets/ (any accidental plaintext decrypt); never commit age keys.
secrets/*
!secrets/*.enc.yaml
!secrets/README.md
!secrets/sync-to-server.sh
*.dec.yaml
*.decrypted
keys.txt
age-key*.txt
